{"tid":1949321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日累計本港累計有641宗確診啦","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T01:16:59.000Z","uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b24d286322885fa0abfd228576476eb7a2cb7b61","tid":1949321,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"2020-03-29 明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200329/s00001/1585470995793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200329%2Fs00001%2F1585470995793&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=25f84a84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200329%2Fs00001%2F1585470995793&h=39c051bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200329/s00001/1585470995793</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/29/TkWQr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F29%2FTkWQr3.jpg&h=9cf2f1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港今日（29日）新增59宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，包括29女30男，介乎11至77歲；本港累計有641宗確診。<br />\n<br />\n新增個案中，40人有外遊紀錄，曾到英國、歐洲及美國等，當中包括18名學生；19名無外遊紀錄的確診者中，7人是已知確診者的密切接觸者，3人曾到酒吧All Night Long。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>酒吧群組：</strong><br />\n．3人（個案614、615、625）曾到酒吧All Night Long<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n．3人（個案627、635、638）為酒吧工作人員<br />\n<br />\n．1人（個案630）為表演者，是個案432的密切接觸者<br />\n<br />\n衛生署衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君稱，新增個案中有6人未找到感染源頭，部分人曾到位於尖沙嘴、中環蘇豪、西營盤及銅鑼灣的酒吧，但她強調眾人於潛伏期到過酒吧聚會，不代表是傳染途徑。"},{"pid":"2f909047f62389f15575b95e55804d1d424391a5","tid":1949321,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"攬炒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk